p.strong: Mechanism: Handling Stale Entries during Page Table Updates

g.text: BEFORE: PTE Updated in RAM, TLB remains Stale
AFTER: Forced Page Walk & Protection Fault
SILENT CORRUPTION: User writes to Read-Only COW page

div.p: VPN: 0xBEEF1 PFN: 0x0042A Perms: R/W=1 (Writable) Status: STALE
PTE @ 0x1F1 PFN: 0x0042A Perms: R/W=0 (Read-Only) Status: UPDATED
